rtion%20By%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2034-year-old%20man%20died%20by%20suicide%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20shortly%20after%20recording%20a%20video%20accusing%20his%20estranged%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20of%20harassment.%20Bengaluru%20police%20have%20also%20found%20a%20suicide%20note%20and%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20following%20a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%2C%20originally%20from%20Bihar%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Manjunath%20Layout%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Neighbours%20found%20him%20hanging%20after%20breaking%20into%20the%20flat.%20A%20placard%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3Bjustice%20is%20due%26quot%3B%20was%20found%20in%20his%20room.%20His%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%20told%20police%20that%20Atul's%20estranged%20wife%20had%20filed%20false%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20his%20parents%20and%20that%20he%20was%20mentally%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20made%20serious%20allegations%20against%20his%20wife%2C%20her%20family%20members%20and%20a%20judge%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jaunpur%20in%20a%20video.%20He%20has%20also%20left%20behind%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20President%2C%20in%20which%20he%20criticised%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20flagged%20a%20trend%20of%20false%20cases.%20In%20another%20note%2C%20he%20has%20said%20he%20pleads%20not%20guilty%20to%20all%20the%20charges%20brought%20against%20him%20by%20his%20wife.%20These%20include%20charges%20under%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%20and%20relevant%20sections%20such%20as%20causing%20hurt%20or%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20%26quot%3BI%20humbly%20request%20the%20court%20to%20stop%20harassing%20my%20parents%20and%20brother%20in%20these%20false%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20he%20recorded%20before%20dying%20by%20suicide%20and%20in%20the%20note%20he%20left%20behind%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20said%20he%20married%20in%202019%20after%20a%20match%20on%20a%20matrimonial%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20she%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20under%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20unnatural%20sex.%20She%20alleged%20that%20he%20demanded%20dowry%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20this%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20father%20and%20he%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20some%20poor%20bollywood%20plot.%20She%20has%20already%20confessed%20that%20her%20father%20was%20suffering%20from%20long%20term%20illness%20in%20her%20cross%20examination.%20Her%20father%20was%20getting%20treated%20from%20AIIMS%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20for%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%20etc.%20Doctors%20gave%20him%20few%20months%20and%20hence%20we%20got%20married%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20This%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20subsequently%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20first%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case%2C%20but%20later%20hiked%20this%20to%20Rs%203%20crore.%20He%20has%20detailed%20a%20court%20exchange%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20when%20he%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20men%20are%20dying%20by%20suicide%20due%20to%20false%20cases%2C%20his%20wife%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20why%20don't%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20judge%20laughed%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20room.%20Atul%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bmust%20think%20about%20his%20family%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20%26quot%3Bsettle%20the%