20Adelaide%20after%20his%20heroics%20in%20Perth.%20If%20one%20looks%20at%20Rohit's%20statistics%20in%20SENA%20(South%20Africa%2C%20England%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia)%2C%20across%20all%20batting%20positions%20in%2046%20completed%20innings%2C%20he%20averages%20a%20shade%20less%20than%2030%20while%20in%2020%20innings%20as%20opener%2C%20he%20scores%20at%2037.8%20thanks%20largely%20to%20the%20successful%20English%20summer%20of%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PTI%20spoke%20to%20a%20BCCI%20Level%203%20coach%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20worked%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%2C%20on%20technical%20aspects%20of%20the%20swashbuckler's%20game%2C%20he%20dissected%20Rohit's%20technique%20to%20explain%20why%20opening%20might%20not%20be%20a%20good%20option%20for%20the%20Indian%20captain%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20Sharma%20has%20had%20very%20limited%20footwork%20all%20his%20career%2C%20even%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20prime.%20Obviously%2C%20at%2037%20and%20half%20years%2C%20the%20reflexes%20have%20slowed%20down%20and%20he%20is%20picking%20the%20length%20a%20trifle%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20qualified%20batting%20coach%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20Rohit%20will%20look%20very%20different%20in%20the%20IPL%20where%20you%20might%20still%20find%20him%20scoring%20a%2035-ball-70%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20with%20opposition%20having%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20mid-130s%20domestic%20bowler%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20why%20is%20No.%206%20better%20for%20Rohit%20in%20the%20third%20Test%3F%20The%20coach%20has%20a%20technical%20response%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Rohit's%20dismissals%20even%20in%20India%2C%20he%20is%20getting%20squared%20up%20more%20often%20than%20not.%20The%20reason%20being%20his%20front-foot%20stride%20is%20becoming%20shorter%20with%20age.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20have%20pronounced%20front-foot%20side%2C%20say%20three%20feet%2C%20you%20are%20able%20to%20cut%20the%20angle%20of%20deviation%20of%20a%20delivery%20off%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20your%20stride%20is%20just%20a%20foot%20and%20quarter%2C%20you%20are%20allowing%20the%20same%20delivery%20to%20shape%20in%20or%20shape%20out.%20So%2C%20a%20world-class%20bowler%20will%20attack%20both%20your%20inside%20edge%20and%20outside%20edge%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20coach%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20opener%2C%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20gave%20his%20reasons%20for%20why%20Rohit%20will%20be%20better%20off%20playing%20at%20No.%206%20at%20the%20Gabba.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20fair%2C%20if%20your%20stride%20is%20shorter%20and%20reflexes%20on%20the%20wane%2C%20the%20Pink%20Kookaburra%20will%20make%20it%20even%20more%20difficult%20for%20you%20to%20survive.%20I%20think%20KL%20had%20said%20before%20the%20game%20that%20it%20comes%20a%20lot%20quicker%20than%20Red%20Kookaburra%20and%20it%20skids%20off%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20his%20current%20footwork%2C%20the%20Red%20Kookaburra%20would%20again%20dart%20around%20and%20seam%20at%20the%20Gabba%20if%20he%20opens.%20If%20he%20comes%20in%20at%20No.%206%2C%20there%20is%20every%20chance%20that%20it%20will%20be%20either%20old%20or%20semi-old%20Kookaburra%20with%20suppressed%20seam%20and%20it%20won't%20do%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20can%20play%20his%20customary%20attacking%20game%20and%20get%20quick%20runs.%20If%20he%20comes%20when%20the%20second%20new%20ball%20is%20taken%2C%20that%20means%20(Mitchell)%20Starc%20and%20(Pat)%20Cummins%20have%20both%20bowled%2025%20odd%20overs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20elaborated%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20Rohit%20was%20reasonably%20successful%20in%20England%20during%20the%202021%20tour%20when%20he%20scored%20his%20only%20Test%20hundred%20in%20a%20SENA%20country%20--%20127%20at%20the%20Oval.%20If%20one%20watches%20his%20performance%20in%20that%20series%2C%20the%20front%20foot%20stride%20to%20cover%20the%20swing%20and%20seam%20movement%20was%20more%20pronounced%20than%20what%20one%20saw%20in%20the%20last%20few%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20in%20England%2C%20the%20ball%20deviates%20at%20a%20bigger%20angle%20compared%20to%20Australia%20and%20at%20times%20even%20with%20a%20shorter%20stride%2C%20one%20might%20just%20edge%20and%20miss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20national%20selector%20Devang%20Gandhi%20put%20forth%20a%20more%20lucid%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20compare%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20Kohli's%20stance.%20Rohit%20has%20a%20wider%20stance%20and%20his%20stride%20won't%20be%20big.%20Virat%20has%20a%20narrow%20stance%20and%20hence%20the%20front%20foot%20stride%20is%20that%20pronounced%20as%20you%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20to%20Rohit's%20batting%20position%2C%20No.%206%20is%20correct%20call%20by%20team%20management.%20There%20isn't%20enough%20data%20in%20SENA%20countries%20to%20suggest%20that%20he%20has%20had%20tremendous%20success%20as%20an%20opener%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20former%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20had%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20Rohit%20to%20come%20at%20the%20top%20as%20he%20looks%20too%20subdued%20in%20the%20middle-order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20reason%20I%20want%20him%20at%20the%20top.%20That's%20where%20he%20can%20be%20aggressive%20and%20expressive.%20Just%20thought%20he%20was%20a%20little%20too%20subdued%2C%20just%20seeing%20his%20body%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20told%20'Star%20Sports'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%20echoed%20the%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20he%20didn't%20make%20runs%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20was%20enough%20on%20the%20field%20there.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20see%20him%20more%20involved%2C%20and%20a%20little%20more%20animated%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe