0commoditized%20and%20if%20you%20do%20want%20to%20be%20one%20of%20those%20players%20that%20are%20a%20provider%20of%20the%20models%2C%20you%20need%20to%20have%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20funding%20and%20you%20need%20to%20be%20a%20company%20that%20is%20losing%20billions%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20and%20it's%20still%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20and%20we%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Perplexity%20CEO%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20decided%20to%20use%20other%20people's%20models%20and%20shape%20them%20to%20be%20really%20good%20for%20end-to-end%20consumer%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-big-tech-ai-spending-race-bottom-margins-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733824862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67573789dc8b666017f2110c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-big-tech-ai-spending-race-bottom-margins-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Salesforce%20CEO%20Benioff's%20plan%3F%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20their%20spending%20to%20make%20my%20products%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sjackson%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Jackson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-big-tech-ai-spending-race-bottom-margins-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20future%20of%20Rupert%20Murdoch's%20media%20empire%20is%20up%20for%20grabs%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20for%20now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rupert%20Murdoch%20in%20a%20car%2C%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757690952dd0818d1a613b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERupert%20Murdoch%20is%2093.%20What%20happens%20to%20the%20media%20empire%20he%20built%20when%20he%20dies%3F%3Cp%3EGilbert%20Carrasquillo%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYup%2C%20it%20was%20right%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BSuccession%26quot%3B%3A%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20and%20his%20son%20Lachlan%2C%20fighting%20three%20other%20Murdoch%20children%20in%20court.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERupert%20and%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20have%20lost%20that%20case%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20means%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20will%20need%20to%20share%20control%20of%20his%20father's%20empire%20with%20three%20siblings%20when%20Rupert%20dies.%20But%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20that%20will%20actually%20mean.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERupert%20Murdoch%20lost%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frupert-murdoch-succession-court-fox-news-corp-david-folkenflik-interview-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20case%20about%20the%20future%20of%20his%20media%20empire%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20does%20that%20mean%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20talk%3A%20It's%20too%20early%20to%20tell.%20At%20least%20one%20appeal%20is%20coming%2C%20so%20this%20could%20all%20shake%20out%20differently%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20now%3A%20It%20means%20that%20Murdoch's%20attempt%20to%20anoint%20his%20son%20Lachlan%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20his%20businesses%20once%20the%20elder%20Murdoch%20dies%20has%20been%20foiled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20that%20holds%20up%2C%20it%20means%20the%20future%20of%20Murdoch's%20empire%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20Fox%20News%20and%20other%20Fox%20TV%20networks%3B%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20and%20the%20New%20York%20Post%3B%20and%20TV%20and%20print%20assets%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Australia%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20that%20much%20messier%20when%20Murdoch%2C%2093%2C%20is%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20ruling%20holds%20up%20%E2%80%94%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20will%20have%20to%20share%20control%20of%20the%20family%20business%20after%20his%20father's%20death%20with%20three%20of%20his%20siblings%3A%20James%2C%20Elisabeth%2C%20and%20Prudence.%20That%20was%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20dispute%20fought%20in%20a%20closed-door%20Nevada%20courtroom%20this%20fall.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F12%2F09%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Frupert-lachlan-murdoch-family-trust.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20its%20hands%20on%20the%20sealed%20ruling%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20probate%20commissioner%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20that%2C%20it's%20very%20hard%20to%20say%20what%20the%20news%20means.%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20has%20argued%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20ran%20the%20family%20business%20the%20way%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20ran%20it.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20would%20keep%20things%20untouched%20once%20his%20father%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20Lachlan%20would%20sell%20some%20assets%20that%20his%20father%20didn't%20want%20to%20sell%20for%20whatever%20reason.%20Maybe%20he%20wouldn't%20run%20Fox%20News%20%E2%80%94%20a%20core%20asset%20for%20the%20family%20business%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20financial%20and%20political%20power%20%E2%80%94%20exactly%20the%20way%20his%20father%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20winners%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%94%20Lachlan's%20siblings%20James%2C%20Elisabeth%2C%20and%20Prudence%20%E2%80%94%20now%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20out-vote%20Lachlan.%20Which%20means%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20that%20they%20could%20force%20sales%20of%20things%20neither%20Lachlan%20nor%20Rupert%20wanted%20to%20part%20with.%20They%20could%20also%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20change%20the%20way%20Fox%20News%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20because%20three%20members%20of%20the%20Murdoch%20clan%20fought%20their%20father's%20plans%20to%20make%20Lachlan%20more%20powerful%20than%20them%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20would%20always%20work%20together.%20The%20ruling%20just%20means%20they%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20weigh%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20rep%2C%20James%2C%20Prudence%2C%20and%20Elisabeth%20applauded%20the%20decision%20and%20offered%20%26quot%3Bhope%20that%20we%20can%20move%20beyond%20this%20litigation%20to%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20and%20rebuilding%20relationships%20among%20all%20family%20members.%26quot%3B%20I%20also%20contacted%20Rupert%20and%20Lachlan%20Murdoch's%20rep%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realize%20that%20this%20is%20shrug-emoji%20of%20an%20explainer%20may%20be%20disappointing%20to%20some%20of%20you%20who%20would%20like%20a%20more%20definitive%20answer.%20Particularly%20those%20of%20you%20whose%20interest%20in%20the%20Murdoch%20family%2C%20and%20its%20twists%20and%20turns%2C%20relates%20primarily%20to%20the%20way%20it%20was%20partially%20fictionalized%20in%20%26quot%3BSuccession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20here's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20reward%20for%20dedicated%20watchers%20of%20HBO%20prestige%20dramas%3A%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20court%20case%2C%20referred%20to%20by%20almost%20everyone%20as%20%26quot%3Bstraight%20out%20of%20Succession%26quot%3B%20was%20literally%20straight%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BSuccession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20reports%20that%20the%20Murdoch%20family%20fight%20kicked%20off%20in%20April%202023%20as%20the%20HBO%20series%20was%20headed%20toward%20its%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3ESetting%20off%20these%20discussions%20was%20the%20episode%20of%20the%20HBO%20drama%20'Succession%2C'%20the%20commissioner%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20patriarch%20of%20the%20family%20dies%2C%20leaving%20his%20family%20and%20business%20in%20chaos.%26quot%3B%20The%20episode%20prompted%20Elisabeth's%20representative%20to%20the%20trust%2C%20Mark%20Dev