ow%20we%20think%20%E2%80%94%20and%20don't%20think%20%E2%80%94%20about%20our%20work.%20From%20startup%20pitches%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-elon-musk-is-right-on-wasteful-defense-spending-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPentagon%3C%2Fa%3E%20procurement%20timetables%2C%20from%20quarterly%20board%20meetings%20to%20annual%20harassment%20trainings%2C%20billions%20of%20presentations%20are%20given%20each%20year%20in%20a%20single%20rigid%2C%20information-squishing%20format%2C%20on%20PowerPoint%20or%20its%20imitators%20Keynote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-employees-laid-off-advice-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Slides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadobe-figma-calls-off-acquisition-merger-technology-antitrust-competition-cma-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFigma%20Slides%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Humanity%20continues%20to%20cram%20compelling%20and%20vital%20information%20into%20single-idea%20slides%2C%20strip%20these%20ideas%20of%20context%2C%20and%20read%20them%20aloud%20among%20a%20flurry%20of%20GIFs%2C%20charts%2C%20and%20animated%20wipes%20and%20swipes.%20Rarely%20does%20the%20deck%20%E2%80%94%20which%20by%20design%20dictates%20a%20one-sided%20style%20of%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20elicit%20robust%20questions%20from%20or%20conversation%20with%20the%20audience.%20We%20are%20constantly%20pitching%20our%20bosses%2C%20their%20bosses%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20each%20other%20via%20a%20one-size%20rhetorical%20tool%20that%20doesn't%20really%20fit%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20are%20finally%20thinking%20outside%20the%20deck.%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-clinton-altman-bezos-say-about-elon-musk-dealbook-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20and%20military%20top%20brass