mate%20action%2C%20menstrual%20health%20and%20education%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-1-1732888782.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-1-1732888782-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-1-1732888782-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-1-1732888782-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-1-1732888782-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384703%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20advocates%20for%20climate%20action%2C%20menstrual%20health%20and%20education%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F166481%2Fbengaluru-sustainability-menstruation-cup-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteam%20conducts%20workshops%20%3C%2Fa%3Eeducating%20children%20about%20sustainable%20habits%20within%20their%20homes.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20using%20cloth%20bags%20instead%20of%20polythene%20bags%3B%20metal%20bottles%20instead%20of%20plastic%20bottles%3B%20and%20public%20transport%20instead%20of%20private%20vehicles.%20All%20actions%20are%20directed%20towards%20reducing%20carbon%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20urge%20them%20to%20ask%20their%20parents%20to%20move%20towards%20renewable%20energy%2C%20adopt%20solar%20panels%20and%20thus%20minimise%20their%20electricity%20bill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20mindsets%20is%20palpable%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20Sandy%20has%20carried